  <name>Pinba Engine (MariaDB 10.11)</name>
  <summary>Pinba storage engine plugin built for MariaDB 10.11</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      This package provides ha_pinba.so compiled against MariaDB 10.11 server
      headers (the default MariaDB on Ubuntu 24.04 LTS). Pinba collects and
      processes application runtime statistics sent over UDP by Pinba clients,
      most commonly the Pinba PHP extension, and exposes them through ordinary
      SQL as real-time reports.
    </p>
  </description>

